

fortune                      Command                      fortune




Print random selected, hopefully humorous, text

/uussrr/ggaammeess/ffoorrttuunnee [ _f_i_l_e ]

fortune prints a message  that is randomly selected from the con-
tents of a  text file.  fortune reads file if  it is named on the
command   line;   otherwise,    it   reads   the   default   file
/usr/games/lib/fortunes.

***** Files *****

/uussrr/ggaammeess/lliibb/ffoorrttuunneess -- Default fortunes

